From: Joshua Gatley-Dewing <joshgatdew@proton.me>
Date: Sun, 31 May 2026 18:46:07 +0000
Subject: linux71

Probably unhelpfull, but this allowed dkms to build on kernel 7.1.
---
 src/wl/sys/wl_cfg80211_hybrid.c | 52 ++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++++---
 1 file changed, 48 insertions(+), 4 deletions(-)

diff --git a/src/wl/sys/wl_cfg80211_hybrid.c b/src/wl/sys/wl_cfg80211_hybrid.c
index 26e10b1..3f37691 100644
